	<message label="005" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Aha" target="actor" targetSpec="" />然后，在某一时刻！<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />之前投稿的咨询<delay20 />
