<anim id="QuestionMark" target="actor" targetSpec="" />顺便问一下，你会投稿什么样的内容呀？</message>
	<message label="007" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><colour id="1" />向喜欢的人告白的时候，<delay8 />
