	<message label="101" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="0" />所以说，<delay20 />
恋爱和早餐，最重要的是注意均衡！</message>
	<message label="102" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />早上比较忙的时候，<delay20 />
我都是随便吃点东西就算了<tag a="110" b="0" /><pageBreak /><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不过看来并不是只要吃了就好，<delay20 />
同时也要注重<delay20 />
饮食均衡呢。<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="103" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="WrySmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><delay frames="16" />呵呵呵，<delay20 />虽然今天早上也很匆忙，<delay8 />
但我有摄取理想的早餐哦。<tag a="110" b="6" />。<pageBreak /><tag a="110" b="0" /><anim id="Surprised" target="actor" targetSpec="" />啊，糟了～！<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Frantic" target="actor" targetSpec="" />早上手忙脚乱的，<delay20 />
忘记穿上裤子啦～！<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="104" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />这样啊<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay frames="40" />
<colour id="4" />不过你好像平时就没有穿<tag a="110" b="0" /><colour id="65535" /><delay20 /></message>
	<message label="201" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Serious" target="actor" targetSpec="" />有秘密更好<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay20 />
恋爱这回事呢，<delay20 />
<anim id="Grin" target="actor" targetSpec="" />会因为秘密而热烈呀。<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="202" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Hesitate" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我这人<delay8 />不太会隐瞒事情，<delay frames="30" />
所以不太能理解<tag a="110" b="0" /><pageBreak /><anim id="Serious" target="actor" targetSpec="" />比起这个，<delay8 />你刚刚挂在嘴边的“<tag a="110" b="6" />”，<delay20 />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />是<tag a="110" b="31" arg="0xcd00" /><tag a="110" b="13" />你的口头禅吗？<delay frames="30" />
听起来很不错呢！</message>
	<message label="203" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />是这样吗？<delay20 />
那么，<delay8 />你要不要试试和我用
<anim id="QuestionMark" target="actor" targetSpec="" />同样的口头禅？<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="204" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Eh" target="actor" targetSpec="" />咦，<delay8 />真的可以吗？<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />那我现在就来用用看哦！<pageBreak /><size value="150" /><anim id="Cheering" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><delay20 /><tag a="110" b="31" arg="0xcd00" /><tag a="110" b="13" /><delay20 />
<anim id="Cheering" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><delay20 />是笨蛋——！<delay20 /><tag a="110" b="6" />。<size value="100" /><pageBreak /><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />呵呵，<delay20 />这个口头禅<tag a="110" b="0" />
果然很棒呢。<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="205" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />嗯，<delay8 />还挺不错的吧？<delay frames="40" />
<colour id="4" />虽然不明白你为什么要说这句话<tag a="110" b="0" /><colour id="65535" /></message>
